data.name: rtbInstructions.Text
data.value: 1. (optional) Select a Magic 8-Ball Service to use (default is a local service with the classic Magic 8-Ball answers). 2. Type a yes/no question to ask the Magic 8-Ball. 3. Press Enter or click the Magic 8-Ball button to ask your question. 4. Wait while the Magic 8-Ball ponders your question, and then the answer will be displayed. 5. (optional) Repeat the above steps to ask another question (or if you didn't like the previous answer).
